From cfc0647df7467bb120194b56ebfbfc4944340d56 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilya Gulya <ilya@gulya.me>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 13:22:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] perf#24c2e: WIP DCC2 reader on dyld2 classic path (durability
 commit)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Retarget the DCC2 packed-closure reader from the dyld3 closure path
(launchWithClosure) to the dyld2 classic path that Darling actually
launches through. Guarded by DARLING_DYLD_DCC2.

- dyld3/DCC2Reader.{h,cpp}: shared singleton, isDCC2Image (exact,
  addr==_arena+image_vmbase), applyAllFixupsOnce (whole-cache single
  apply, hard-fail on loc-not-RW / unknown-kind / unresolved-extern),
  counters + dumpCounters.
- src/dyld2.cpp: initShared() after main-exe instantiate; dccTryLoad()
  hook at top of load() substituting cached images.
- src/ImageLoaderMachOCompressed.cpp: guarded-if in rebase() (apply DCC2
  fixups once) and doBind() (skip; hard-fail if fixups not yet applied).
- dyld3/Loading.{cpp,h}: dyld3-path DCC2 edits wrapped in #if BUILDING_DYLD
  (fixes libdyld.dylib link — Loading.cpp is in both loader targets).

WIP: 2-dylib live smoke still crashes in instantiateFromCache (scattered
LINKEDIT pointer math) — task #91 open. Committed for durability so the
work survives checkout/handoff; NOT yet exported to a patch profile.
