 	if ( this->usablePrebinding(context) ) {
 		// skip rebasing because prebinding is valid

From 2d46a6bc1e761a31250deb853507cb18886966d5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilya Gulya <ilya@gulya.me>
